Verus Library Minimizer
=======================
This minimizer is only possible due to the phenomenal speed of verification
in Verus. Thanks Verus team!

Logging to: /home/milnes/projects/APAS-VERUS/analyses/veracity-minimize-lib.log

Arguments:
  -c, --codebase:     /home/milnes/projects/APAS-VERUS
  -l, --library:      /home/milnes/projects/APAS-VERUS/src/vstdplus
  -F, --file:         (all files)
  -n, --dry-run:      true
  -b, --broadcasts:   false
  -L, --lib-broadcasts: false
  -N, --max-lemmas:   all
  -a, --asserts:      false
  -A, --max-asserts:  all
  -p, --proof-blocks: false
  -P, --max-proof-blocks: all
  -e, --exclude:      (none)
  -f, --fail-fast:    false
  --danger:           false
  --project:          APAS

Mode: full crate verification (estimated 90-120s per iteration)

